{title: Knockin' on Heaven's Door}
{artist: Bob Dylan}
{key: G}
{tempo: 68}
{time: 4/4}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]Mama, take this [D]badge off of [Am]me
[G]I can't use it [D]any[C]more
[G]It's getting dark, too [D]dark to [Am]see
[G]Feels like I'm [D]knockin' on heaven's [C]door
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[G]Knock, knock, [D]knockin' on [Am]heaven's door
[G]Knock, knock, [D]knockin' on [C]heaven's door
{end_of_chorus}
